T1  - Are outsiders handicapped in CEO successions?
AU  - Agrawal, Anup
AU  - Knoeber, Charles R.
AU  - Tsoulouhas, Theofanis
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 12
IS  - 3
SP  - 619
